	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Mega Man 9 &quot;Alternate Soundtrack&quot;</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I've been working on this for awhile... however, my HDD crashed and I lost all the MMLs of it, so instead of trying to reconstruct them, I'm just going to release them.  This is not really an official release, as Plug Man, Jewel Man, Final Boss, and a few minor songs aren't done yet, but I'm not sure I'll do Plug/Jewel mans since 1) i can't think of anything to do for them, and 2) I actually like the originals anyway.
<br />
<br />This project is basically a "what if i wrote the music for Mega Man 9" idea.  
<br />
<br />These NSFs are all I have left of the project right now.  Ones that are slightly older copies of songs that got lost will have an asterisk next to them.
<br />
<br /><a href="http://4x86.com/title.nsf" class="postlink">Title</a>
<br /><a href="http://4x86.com/boss_intro.nsf" class="postlink">Boss Selected*</a>
<br /><a href="http://4x86.com/magma.nsf" class="postlink">Magma Man*</a>
<br /><a href="http://4x86.com/galaxy.nsf" class="postlink">Galaxy Man</a>
<br /><a href="http://4x86.com/tornado.nsf" class="postlink">Tornado Man</a>
<br /><a href="http://4x86.com/splash.nsf" class="postlink">Splash Woman</a>
<br /><a href="http://4x86.com/concrete.nsf" class="postlink">Concrete Man*</a>
<br /><a href="http://4x86.com/hornet.nsf" class="postlink">Hornet Man</a>
<br /><a href="http://4x86.com/boss.nsf" class="postlink">Boss</a>
<br /><a href="http://4x86.com/wily1.nsf" class="postlink">Wily Castle 1 (sounds familiar..with some new touches)</a>
<br /><a href="http://4x86.com/wily2.nsf" class="postlink">Wily Castle 2</a>
<br /><a href="http://4x86.com/wily3.nsf" class="postlink">Wily Castle 3 (may sound familiar to like 2 people)</a>
<br /><a href="http://4x86.com/plug.nsf" class="postlink">Plug Man (very unfinished, includes some melody from the actual plug man song)</a>
<br />
<br />enjoy...  i still plan on doing final boss, possibly finishing plug/jewel, and definitely finishing small themes (like stage select and wily castle intro).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


