	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It's really cool, however I have to say that the music really doesn't have that Mega Man feel to it. The soundtrack sounds more like something that Konami would put out than Capcom, which really isn't a bad thing.
<br />
<br />I made a mistake when I was making my own variation of the Mega Man boss selection theme, that I sort of noticed you made as well. Mega Man 2's boss selection theme has a "doodoot dodoo doooo.. dododoot dodoo dooo" going on, where it should be "dododoot" both times, the first time only has two notes because the first note is cut off by the "boss selected" sound effect" Very odd, I think. However MM9 got it right when it "remade" the song.
<br />
<br />Anyway, good job on the music, enjoyed listening to it all!

		

		</td>
	</tr>
