	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I'm most enamored with your Galaxy Man track.
<br />
<br />I have to admit that the triangle taking the lead at :32 in, followed by a neat duty-cycling effect at :37 (an effect that was never used in any mega man music if I recall correctly) doesn't sound very Mega Man-y to me. It sounds like Rushjet1 to me and I LOVE it.  <img src="./images/smilies/icon_biggrin.gif" alt=":D" title="Very Happy" />
<br />
<br />Although I'd like to add that any moments that 'don't sound' Mega Man like to me, is just me being as hairsplitting as possible. Of a lot of nsf composers out there I'd nominate some of your stuff as pulling off the most Mega Man-like sound I've heard.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
